<table border="0" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td colspan="1" valign="top" align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="5" color="black">
    Invisibility</font></td>
    <td colspan="2" valign="top" align="left"><font color="black"><img
    src="http://205.229.72.28/ev1/public_html/images/magic.gif" width="216" height="30" align="right"></font></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td colspan = "3">
    <!--<a href="magic.asp?mode=updateform&amp;ID=161">-->
    <a href="../UserUpdate.asp?ID=161">
    <small><font color="#000080" face="Verdana"><strong>Add New Info Here</strong></font></small>
    </a>
    </td>
    
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
    <b>Description:</b> <br>
    Invisiblity allows your character to become invisible. You will not be seen my most creatures while in this state. The unfortunate part of it is that you will lose it if you cast a spell or attack a creature. You may talk while invisible and still retain the effect however. All undead and very high level mobs will see through invis.<BR>
<BR>
<B>Location:</B><BR>General<br>
    <b>Effects:</b><br>
    Invisibility--Non Undead only
    </font>
    
    </td>
    <td rowspan="2" valign="top" align="right"><font
    face="verdana" color="black" size="1">
    
			&nbsp;<br>
			&nbsp;<br>
			Mana:<br>
			Casting Time:<br>
			Target Type:<br>
			Level:<br>
			Rank:<br>
    </font></td>
    <td rowspan="2" valign="top" align="right"><font
    face="verdana" color="black" size="1">

		  &nbsp;<br>
		  &nbsp;<br>
			30<br>
			5<br>
			Target<br>
			4<br>
			2<br>
    </font></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
    <b>Availble to:</b></font><br>
    
					<a href='http://www.everlore.com/races_classes/classes.asp?CID=3&mode=details&type=races'>Enchanter</a>, <a href='http://www.everlore.com/races_classes/classes.asp?CID=10&mode=details&type=races'>Magician</a>, <a href='http://www.everlore.com/races_classes/classes.asp?CID=19&mode=details&type=races'>Wizard</a>, <a href='http://www.everlore.com/races_classes/classes.asp?CID=17&mode=details&type=races'>Shaman</a>
    
     </font>
    
