	<tr>
		
			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Invisibility is essential for corpse retrieval in dangerous areas.  While most actions cancel the invisibility spell, the /corpse command does not.  This command moves your corpse to you, as long as you are fairly near the corpse to begin with.<BR>
<BR>
Approach your corpse invisible.  Drag it somewhere safe by using /corpse, backing up, and repeating.  Actually looting your corpse will cancel the ivisibility spell, so several repetitions of backup and /corpse are usually advisable.<BR>

				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
	<tr>
		
			<td bgcolor="#D6D1BE">	
		
	
