			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				A note on undead and invisibility, above. Undead that have not been activated and are waiting cannot see through undead. Most undead cannot see through invisibility at all. However, higher level activated undead (like ghouls, maybe others) seem to sometimes be able to see through the spell. But I have gained many levels in Befallen, using invisibility, and it is the exception, not the rule, for undead to be able to see through the spell.
				</font>
			</td>

