				Note on the dragging body bit. Ignore the whole backup method. Set /corpse to a hotkey (done by going into socials and right clicking on one of the buttons) and then just run by yoour body and begin to hit the key repeatedly. It will drag your body behind you. Much better for evacs from hostile territory :P
